reviews.text: A good place to chill. Bar snack are yummy!! They also make really good drinks like old fashion, Manhattan...etc  recommend the Lemongrass-Toni.
By far my favorite hidden gem bar. Friendly staff and a cool, non pretentious interior with reasonably volumed throwback music. My go-to for a chill night.
Slightly too expensive for the beers and liquors price. Decoration is nice tho. Good place to hang out
Lovely little pub with great lunch time menu.
Chill vibes. Nice deco. Cocktails are just ok.
